c: 59
v: 23
t: "Woh Allah hi hai jiske siwa koi maabood nahin woh Badshah hai, nihayat muqaddas , sarasar salamati (all-peace), aman dene wala( Giver of security), nigehbaan, sab par ghalib, apna hukum ba-zoar naafiz karne wala, aur bada hi hokar rehne wala. Paak hai Allah us shirk se jo log kar rahey hain"